00:21:32.003 --> 00:21:33.319
...dengan usaha minimal!

00:21:33.467 --> 00:21:35.334
Kebenaran tentang itu tidak terungkap...

00:21:35.611 --> 00:21:37.266
...dan Rupa juga menghilang.

00:21:37.776 --> 00:21:39.942
Kami menipu Thakuma.

00:21:44.216 --> 00:21:45.932
Sayangku.

00:21:46.092 --> 00:21:47.998
Ini bukan hanya ide Bondita...

00:21:48.118 --> 00:21:49.615
...itu berhasil.

00:21:49.922 --> 00:21:51.610
Bersamaan dengan itu...

00:21:51.730 --> 00:21:53.401
...kita harus melihat...

00:21:53.549 --> 00:21:56.076
...Wajah Thakuma yang menakutkan.

00:21:57.898 --> 00:21:59.255
Sayangku, dia...

00:21:59.375 --> 00:22:01.868
...lidah pedasnya tenang.

00:22:02.369 --> 00:22:03.913
Itu macet.

00:22:04.510 --> 00:22:06.497
Saya merasa seperti...

00:22:06.674 --> 00:22:08.646
...pergi dan bertanya padanya...

00:22:10.626 --> 00:22:11.925
...itu...

00:22:12.114 --> 00:22:15.738
...haruskah aku
menjulurkan lidahmu?

